OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1784751302
OL,3,CLewisham council could become the
OL,4,Cfirst in the UK to resist immigration
OL,5,Craids
OL,7,FLewisham council could be the first in
OL,8,Fthe UK to ban its administration from
OL,9,Fcooperating with the Home Office on
OL,10,Fimmigration raids.
OL,12,FA motion is being debated today, which
OL,13,Fwould commit the Green run council to
OL,14,Fsystematically review its work with
OL,15,Fimmigration enforcement and refuse to
OL,16,Fassist raids "wherever legally
OL,17,Fpossible".
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/9
