PN,37402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1784751302
OL,3,CLewisham council could become the
OL,4,Cfirst in the UK to resist immigration
OL,5,Craids
OL,7,FThe mayor of Lewisham, Liam
OL,8,FShrivastava says it is part of the
OL,9,Fcouncil's attempts to "protect our
OL,10,Fdiverse communities from Labour's anti-
OL,11,Fmigrant onslaught."
OL,13,FHe told ITV News London:
OL,15,F"This motion is about being really
OL,16,Fclear that we are going to protect
OL,17,Feveryone in our community, and that
OL,18,Fincludes migrant workers.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1784751302
OL,3,CLewisham council could become the
OL,4,Cfirst in the UK to resist immigration
OL,5,Craids
OL,7,F"The motion makes very clear that we
OL,8,Fare London's first borough of
OL,9,Fsanctuary, we're very proud of that
OL,10,Fbut we don't just want to be a borough
OL,11,Fof sanctuary in name but also in
OL,12,Fpractice."
OL,14,FThe motion further commits Lewisham to
OL,15,Fworking with Lambeth and other Green-
OL,16,Fled councils to build an anti-raids
OL,17,F"Sanctuary corridor" across London.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1784751302
OL,3,CLewisham council could become the
OL,4,Cfirst in the UK to resist immigration
OL,5,Craids
OL,7,FThis would involve collaborating with
OL,8,Fmigrant organisations, anti-raids
OL,9,Fnetworks, law centres, faith and
OL,10,Fcommunity groups to share best
OL,11,Fpractise and policies.
OL,13,FShrivasta continued:
OL,15,F"We welcome refugees, we have good
OL,16,Fworking relationships with migration
OL,17,Forganizations supporting refugees and
OL,18,Fasylum seekers. We have officers
OL,19,Fdedicated to that work.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1784751302
OL,3,CLewisham council could become the
OL,4,Cfirst in the UK to resist immigration
OL,5,Craids
OL,7,F"But what we're wanting to do is
OL,8,Freally extend the concept of being a
OL,9,Fsanctuary borough, making sure that
OL,10,Fthose practices and those values are
OL,11,Fembedded across all council services."
OL,13,FThe motion argues that sharing council
OL,14,Fdata with the Home Office for
OL,15,Fimmigration enforcement is
OL,16,Fincompatible with those values.
OL,18,FIt comes after a 77% rise in illegal
OL,19,Fworking raids since Labour came to
OL,20,Fpower.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
