FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1784751302
OL,3,CLewisham council could become the
OL,4,Cfirst in the UK to resist immigration
OL,5,Craids
OL,7,FThere were 261 raids in Lewisham alone
OL,8,Flast year.
OL,10,FThe motion would see administration
OL,11,Fworking with Lewisham Anti-Raids to
OL,12,Fsupport migrant businesses and those
OL,13,Ftargeted by raids, to ensure they are
OL,14,Faware of their legal rights in
OL,15,Frelation to immigration enforcement.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1784751302
OL,3,CLewisham council could become the
OL,4,Cfirst in the UK to resist immigration
OL,5,Craids
OL,7,FIt would also work with organisations
OL,8,Fin the Lewisham Migration Forum to
OL,9,Fstrengthen "trauma-informed, anti-
OL,10,Fracist, care and evidence based
OL,11,Fapproaches" to better support migrant
OL,12,Fcommunities.
OL,14,FIt wants to conduct a comprehensive
OL,15,Freview into Council systems and
OL,16,Fprocesses to ensure that resources and
OL,17,Fmoney are not spent on facilitating
OL,18,F"harm to our communities".
OL,20,FA Home Office spokesperson said:
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
