PN,37408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1784751302
OL,3,CLewisham council could become the
OL,4,Cfirst in the UK to resist immigration
OL,5,Craids
OL,7,F"While all immigration enforcement
OL,8,Fvisits are intelligence led, we make
OL,9,Fno apology for joining forces with
OL,10,Flocal authorities to enable
OL,11,Finformation sharing and ultimately
OL,12,Ffighting criminals who fuel
OL,13,Fimmigration crime.
OL,15,F"Since coming into power, we have
OL,16,Fincreased Immigration Enforcement
OL,17,Faction to the highest level in British
OL,18,Fhistory.
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOU
