OL,3,CLewisham council could become the
OL,4,Cfirst in the UK to resist immigration
OL,5,Craids
OL,7,F"This has delivered an 83% rise in
OL,8,Fillegal working arrests and 77% rise
OL,9,Fin raids between 1 July 2024 to 31
OL,10,FDecember 2025."
